<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>RARCrack-MaykelMillan</title>
    <hta:application 
        id="rarcrack"
        applicationname="RARCrack"
        border="thin"
        borderstyle="normal"
        caption="yes"
        icon="shell32.dll,43"
        maximizebutton="yes"
        minimizebutton="yes"
        sysmenu="yes"
        scroll="yes"
        singleinstance="yes"
        showintaskbar="yes"
        windowstate="normal"
    />
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #9933FF;
            color: white;
        }
        .container {
            width: 400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }
        .title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .subtitle {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .button {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #FF9900;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #FF6600;
        }
        input[type="text"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 16px;
            border: none;
        }
        .output {
            margin-top: 20px;
            background-color: #660099;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display: none;
        }
        .output p {
            margin: 0;
        }
        #progressBar {
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #FF6600;
            height: 20px;
            display: none;
        }
        #progress {
            width: 0%;
            height: 100%;
            background-color: #FF9900;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 20px;
            color: black;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="title">Bienvenido a RARCrack</div>
        <div class="subtitle">Si se logra encontrar la contraseña correcta los archivos se extraeran automaticamente en "Extraction".</div>

        <label for="ip">Introduce el archivo cifrado:</label>
        <input type="text" id="ip" placeholder="Enter IP">

        <button class="button" onclick="startGeolocalization()">Empezar ataque de diccionario</button>
        <button class="button" onclick="closeHTA()">Cerrar</button>

        <div id="progressBar">
            <div id="progress">0%</div>
        </div>

        <div id="output" class="output">
            <p id="info"></p>
            <p id="mapsLink"></p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function startRARCrack() {
